message.entry: Specify a triangle connectivity matrix followed by x, y, and z co-ordinates, or a triangulation or delaunayTriangulation object.
The triangulation must be composed of triangles.
The triangulation must reside in 3D space.
The triangulation must be composed of tetrahedra.
2-D triangulations are not supported. Specify a 3-D triangulation or use triplot for 2-D.
